snippet.title: Wolfenstein | Blade of Agony Chapter 3 - The "Eder Damn" overhaul: What's new?
snippet.description:
In this developer video of 'Blade of Agony' Chapter 3, the project lead Daniel 'Tormentor667' talks about the improvements that have been made on the existing maps in Chapter 1+2 while playing the "Eder Dam, Operation: Chastice.

Get some insight information about what the team has been doing all the time to make sure, it is worth it to replay the original chapters before you jump into the final confrontation with Hitler and his henchmen. Get psyched!
